10-403.County and city bonds; proposition; rate of interest.

The proposition shall state the rate of interest such bond shall draw.

SourceLaws 1869, § 3, p. 92;R.S.1913, § 407;C.S.1922, § 324;C.S.1929, § 11-403;R.S.1943, § 10-403;Laws 2023, LB92, § 44.
